metadata.name: Ben Unbothered OG #1/50
metadata.description:
Ben Unbothered OG #1 to 50 includes a variety of Unlockables:

Unlockables 1:

Includes a 3D OG Ben PFP NFT
Includes Downloadable Content on the official website of: OG MP4 File, 4-8 PFPs and Images (Only accessible through connecting the wallet that holds the NFT)


Unlockables 2:

Tier 1 Whitelist - Access List to The Ben Unbothered Pilot 2D Illustrated Collection
First 50 Priced NFTs: No #1 to #50 include a limited edition unlockable figurine (Ben Unbothered OG Metallic )

Whitelist/Access List Tiers:

Tier 1: Can Mint 5 days before public sales + 3 Mints per wallet (TBD)
Tier 2: Can Mint 3 days before public sales + 2 Mints per wallet
Tier 3: Can Mint 1 day before public sales + 2 Mints per wallet
